GridTreeControl - Product Showcase
</Paragraph> 
<Paragraph>
    The GridTreeControl serves as a multi-column tree control that is optimized to display tens and thousands of items. This control uses a load-on-demand architecture and quickly generates the tree view. You can toggle the view of the underlying nodes by clicking the plus-minus glyphs of a root node. It provides complete customization options. It can be used in applications that deals with hierarchical data. Following samples will showcases the real-time applications on which the GridTreeControl can be used.
</Paragraph> 

<Paragraph> <Bold>File Explorer</Bold>-This sample showcases how a File Explorer application can be created by using GridTreeControl.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph> <Bold>Organization Tree</Bold>-This sample showcases how an Organization's employee hierarchy can be displayed by using GridTreeControl.</Paragraph>

